title: I want to help you be happy just trust me, you can trust me c'mon dear, I won't let anybody hurt you...

attachments.displayName: I want to help you be happy just trust me, you can trust me c'mon dear, I won't let anybody hurt you I won't hurt you, That's it come to me and grab my hand, squeeze it tightly I will take you away from these judgmental beings , I will hold you so tight and lead you out of the dark tunnel, can you see it?
